I fixed adding deps on BUILD file under "./tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/data/" as below.

28 tf_custom_op_library(
29 name = "_prefetching_ops.so",
30 srcs = ["ops/prefetching_ops.cc"],
31 deps = [
32 "//tensorflow/contrib/data/kernels:prefetching_kernels",
